{"tid":686652,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"法國總統：施丹激勵我們的年輕人 希望他能為國家擔任重要角色","createTime":"2018-06-01T13:11:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T11:52:52.000Z","uid":10338,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8f67112bb8ece032304639c79c9d528eda53c1cc","tid":686652,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T13:11:19.000Z","msg":"法國總統馬克龍在近日接受《巴黎人報》採訪時表示，自己希望施丹能在國家擔任重要角色。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;不論作為球員還是教練，他取得的成績都是非凡的。他能激勵我們的年輕人，能讓所有人走上正確的軌道，我希望他能為國家擔任某個重要角色。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n馬克龍的話也許有某種深意？目前還不得而知。雖然施丹在過去比較謹慎地表達過自己的政治立場，但他在2002年前後，以及去年的法國大選期間，曾公開抵制法國極右翼的國民陣線參選人讓-瑪利-勒龐，以及去年與馬克龍一道競選總統的讓-瑪利-勒龐的女兒，瑪琳-勒龐。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我的理念和2002年時一樣，我的思想和國民陣線相去甚遠，極端右翼總是不好的。&rdquo;施丹在去年法國大選期間曾這樣說。<br />\n<br />\n選埋總統 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e07dcc81d47f8d3fd049fa00cf7eecf0e94bda89","tid":686652,"uid":20522,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T13:13:10.000Z","msg":"賓斯馬係馬卡龍老友嚟<br />\n即係法國總統都係佢嘅人"},{"pid":"12fef94bf5b3bdd8dac714537011b0cd492ebd5d","tid":686652,"uid":26389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T13:40:58.000Z","msg":"拖舟係阿拉伯人<br />\n法國政府唔會比佢擔任重要職位的<br />\n就算唔係穆斯林都唔得"},{"pid":"7d95a3a4be0767af718cae04c7ff5042cca01e9b","tid":686652,"uid":102826,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T13:56:42.000Z","msg":"的確幾激勵，踢到咁廢都可以留喺皇馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe29a52b53f31040417c61667c13916ceaf0251","tid":686652,"uid":36178,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:08:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賓斯馬係馬卡龍老友嚟<br />\n即係法國總統都係佢嘅人</blockquote><br />\n總統, 拖舟<br />\n副總統, 賓周馬"},{"pid":"f18e1774bc36ac1dd1caeef92e172eeee9fb46ea","tid":686652,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fe29a52b53f31040417c61667c13916ceaf0251","tid":686652,"uid":36178,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:08:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賓斯馬係馬卡龍老友嚟<br />\n即係法國總統都係佢嘅人</blockquote><br />\n總統, 拖舟<br />\n副總統, 賓周馬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T16:20:06.000Z","msg":"法國隊長：賓拖馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f8a045a991c12f5705c0a43da54d3c002d964c6","tid":686652,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d95a3a4be0767af718cae04c7ff5042cca01e9b","tid":686652,"uid":102826,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T13:56:42.000Z","msg":"的確幾激勵，踢到咁廢都可以留喺皇馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:19:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33008b3436778db55e154c37856e8e1abd4bcfd9","tid":686652,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:52:52.000Z","msg":"教國家隊啦，迪甘斯垃撚圾的"}]}